{"tid":54824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一周必看】三醉警當街肉搏三少女　疑鹹豬手掀惡鬥　全部被捕","createTime":"2016-12-26T00:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T01:32:05.000Z","uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"048093b6bd1a9cf137ac4ba9869cc675facb9d7c","tid":54824,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T00:15:40.000Z","msg":"【一周必看】三醉警當街肉搏三少女　疑鹹豬手掀惡鬥　全部被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警隊醜聞停不了！繼有警隊高層捲入性騷擾女下屬事件，4名毒品調查科休班警員，周三(21日)凌晨在旺角夜店消遣後離去，於街頭疑與3名少女碰撞，其中1名少女報稱臀部被摸，懷疑被「鹹豬手」非禮，雙方頓起爭執。在場1名休班警充當「和事老」勸交不成反被打傷，其餘3男警與少女當街混戰，警方到場拘捕涉案的3名休班警及3少女，旺角警區重案組正調查事件。<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19877142&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19877142%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161226&d=FP6j%2BlSK78%2FwI6t89AQszAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=47b7e0b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19877142%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161226&h=1382a5ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19877142&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161226</a>"},{"pid":"33c5cbc2f0ee9789f2ad11348e64ffd39b9e8428","tid":54824,"uid":47426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T00:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bd5d03d0568359ef977de942d26b6af36f3998","tid":54824,"uid":63160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T00:19:07.000Z","msg":"休班警上線啦"},{"pid":"21661ea970c9b6bf5d434ba724367f1a67a5e4b2","tid":54824,"uid":60244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T00:20:47.000Z","msg":"帶曬女 女 女返警署"},{"pid":"6a019a15c9df2d3238a6a5577f0571f88ab445ba","tid":54824,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy